IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. HELLO-WORLD.
AUTHOR .HAWIN.
ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 P PIC 9(5).
01 R PIC 9(2).
01 N PIC 9(5) .
01 AMOUNT PIC 9(5).
01 CI PIC 9(5).

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
ACCEPT P.
ACCEPT R.
ACCEPT N.
COMPUTE AMOUNT=P*(1+(R/100))**N.
DISPLAY 'AMOUNT: ' AMOUNT
COMPUTE CI=AMOUNT - P.
DISPLAY 'CI :' CI.

STOP RUN.

